info:

servers:

      responses:

          description: OK
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/A"

      type: object
      properties:
        propname:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/B"
    B:
      type: object
      properties:
        propname:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/A"
